org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver

Interface MetricsTableAggregateSource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseSource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MetricsTableAggregateSourceImpl

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public interface MetricsTableAggregateSource
extends BaseSource
    This interface will be implemented by a MetricsSource that will export metrics from multiple regions of a table into the hadoop metrics system.
